messages.messageBody:
We (briefly) went to the public exhibit at BrickCon this past weekend.
There was some very cool stuff there and I thought some people might
be interested in seeing pictures. I am posting a link to the flickr
group for BrickCon and also links for some things that I thought were
neat. The main reason I am doing the latter is that there are a lot
of people pics there so if you want to go straight to the LEGOs
without browsing, you might prefer the direct links.

the flickr pool: http://www.flickr.com/groups/nwbrickcon/pool/
